00:13:19,579 --> 00:13:22,702
than any other extreme diet
related death incident, at first.

261
00:13:23,277 --> 00:13:26,931
However, as you would peel an onion

262
00:13:27,077 --> 00:13:30,511
upon deeper digging and further
investigation, we were able to find out

263
00:13:31,087 --> 00:13:34,035
the ultimate truth of the story.

264
00:13:36,093 --> 00:13:41,029
MSC News Times will do our best to bring
you the accurate truth in the future.

265
00:13:41,329 --> 00:13:45,769
