and will not bend the truth.

266
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:46,854
That anchor is good.

267
00:13:46,945 --> 00:13:48,754
That’s very much like MSC.

268
00:13:48,845 --> 00:13:50,429
-That's how news should be.
-It is.

269
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:52,587
That is all for the night
from MSC News Times.

270
00:13:53,093 --> 00:13:53,927
Thank you.

271
00:14:53,193 --> 00:14:56,360
People believe that a Pinocchio is
