274
00:15:03,454 --> 00:15:06,655
Pinocchios and reporters
should've been aware of that.

275
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:09,909
The fact that people believe whatever
they say unconditionality, so...

276
00:15:10,981 --> 00:15:13,822
They should've been awared of how much more
