277
00:15:15,594 --> 00:15:16,428
I know.

278
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:18,861
I know, but...

279
00:15:19,221 --> 00:15:20,596
They should've been careful...

280
00:15:20,728 --> 00:15:21,870
