more careful than that?

286
00:15:37,801 --> 00:15:39,547
Looking at you, Candidate 444...

287
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:43,399
I now realize the reason
why a Pinocchio...

288
00:15:45,367 --> 00:15:46,331
can't be a reporter.

289
00:15:48,127 --> 00:15:49,820
How dangerous it'd be if
someone who ignores

290
00:15:49,911 --> 00:15:52,397
the fact that they could make
mistake, to become a reporter.

291
00:15:53,411 --> 00:15:55,058
How scary it is to speak recklessly

292
00:15:55,305 --> 00:15:57,675
when not even aware of the
weight their words carry.

293
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:03,394
I see it now.

294
00:16:08,394 --> 00:16:09,228
Are those words...

295
00:16:11,595 --> 00:16:12,595
...directed towards me?

296
00:16:16,427 --> 00:16:17,261
Yes.

297
00:16:50,093 --> 00:16:51,275
You're pathetic.

298
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:53,640
Choi Dal-Po.

299
00:17:01,748 --> 00:17:03,954
Seoul Han River Police Station

300
00:17:05,973 --> 00:17:07,708
Hey, where's Choi Dal-Po?

301
00:17:07,799 --> 00:17:09,208
Why? So you can gloat in his face?

302
00:17:09,299 --> 00:17:10,133
Of course.

303
00:17:10,224 --> 00:17:12,309
You have no idea how he
ignored me all these years.

304
00:17:12,394 --> 00:17:14,004
-So, where is he?
-I don't know.

305
00:17:14,095 --> 00:17:15,329
I couldn't reach him since last night.

306
00:17:15,419 --> 00:17:17,950
I think he's in hiding, so let
me know when you find him.

307
00:17:19,195 --> 00:17:20,029
In hiding?

308
00:17:20,195 --> 00:17:21,096
That's no good.

309
00:17:21,396 --> 00:17:22,796
I have tons to say to him.

310
00:17:25,829 --> 00:17:26,829
My back.

311
00:17:27,195 --> 00:17:28,929
I wonder if I slept wrong last night.

312
00:17:30,028 --> 00:17:31,238
The number you are calling...

313
00:17:31,329 --> 00:17:32,396
-What?
-...is not responding.

314
00:17:32,487 --> 00:17:34,872
-He's refusing my phone call?
-Leave a message after the beep.

315
00:17:34,963 --> 00:17:36,876
14 percent versus 12 percent.

316
