00:17:54,831 --> 00:17:57,042
Let's not look at the viewer
rating for the time being.

324
00:17:57,133 --> 00:17:57,765
But Mr Director,

325
00:17:57,856 --> 00:18:01,708
how can we not pay attention to viewer
ratings when we'll go on against MSC?

326
00:18:01,799 --> 00:18:03,316
There's even not much difference.

327
00:18:04,374 --> 00:18:07,087
