into the battlefield blind.

328
00:18:08,674 --> 00:18:09,711
Guess you're right.

329
00:18:09,802 --> 00:18:11,189
Then, I'll pull it back up.

330
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:11,945
No.

331
00:18:13,230 --> 00:18:14,137
Mr Director.

332
00:18:15,697 --> 00:18:18,784
Okay, let's not fight
and just do our job.

333
00:18:19,164 --> 00:18:21,272
We were too focused on competing
against MSC

334
00:18:21,363 --> 00:18:23,494
that we neglected to uncover
the truth like we used to.

335
00:18:23,972 --> 00:18:27,924
There could be a repeat of this sort
of mistake if we lose our focus again.

336
00:18:28,015 --> 00:18:30,790
So let's forget about competing

337
00:18:30,881 --> 00:18:32,981
for visual, exclusive news
and viewer rating

338
00:18:33,289 --> 00:18:35,489
and pay full attention
to uncover the truth.

339
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,542
Is that understood?

340
00:18:36,907 --> 00:18:38,674
-Yes, Sir.
-Yes, Sir.

341
00:18:39,775 --> 00:18:41,122
