343
00:18:44,588 --> 00:18:46,329
It was so close.

344
00:18:48,754 --> 00:18:49,512
Seonbae!

345
00:18:49,755 --> 00:18:51,619
Congratulations on winning
the viewer rating.

346
00:18:52,154 --> 00:18:54,821
