939
00:51:40,529 --> 00:51:41,399
She is.

940
00:51:41,529 --> 00:51:42,586
Where did she go suddenly?

941
00:51:58,129 --> 00:51:58,838
Hey.

942
00:51:59,028 --> 00:52:00,762
