999
00:54:39,127 --> 00:54:41,510
Are you out shopping instead
of doing your work?

1000
00:54:42,661 --> 00:54:44,505
No, do you remember Moon Duk-soo?

1001
00:54:44,596 --> 00:54:45,954
The container fire case suspect.

1002
00:54:46,045 --> 00:54:49,479
