1045
00:56:37,278 --> 00:56:40,345
You're going to see, hear, and deliver
a lot of cases in the future.

1046
00:56:41,445 --> 00:56:43,143
Cases that are much more

1047
00:56:43,378 --> 00:56:45,808
difficult to solve and handle
