00:56:47,178 --> 00:56:48,309
I'm wearing a black coat.

1049
00:56:58,378 --> 00:56:59,645
Yes, I see you.

1050
00:57:18,345 --> 00:57:21,227
Cases where you can't make
neither choice nor judgment...

